title: Santa Rita Ranch - Built To Rent Houses!
map_address: 348 Banyon Drive near Mira Mesa Drive
posting_body: ['Caso Santa Rita Ranch', 'Country Living at Caso Santa Rita Ranch', 'This is an 1873 Sq.', 'Ft., 4 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath, Single Family Rental Home.', 'Welcome to Caso Santa Rita Ranch, a brand-new development of built-for-rent houses in the grand-design planned community of Santa Rita Ranch in North Austin.', 'Liberty Hill address and Liberty Hill ISD.', 'You can choose from spacious three-bedroom or four-bedroom rental houses with stylish features, like wood-style flooring and white quartz countertops, and enjoy access to shared amenities and fun community events with the residents living at Santa Rita Ranch.', 'Exclusive Residence Features:', 'Spacious three-bedroom or four-bedroom layouts', 'White shaker cabinets', 'White quartz countertops', 'Single basin kitchen sink', 'Gas stove & range', 'Smart thermostat and video doorbell', 'Dark brown hardwood-style flooring', 'Stainless steel GE appliances', 'Covered back patio', 'Open concept floor plans', 'Fenced backyard', '2 car garage w/ built-in EV charging ports', 'Community Amenities:', 'Clubhouse', 'Two resort-style swimming pools', 'Two splash pads', 'Two two-story waterslides', 'Barbecue barn', 'On-demand fitness classes', 'Cardio and free weights', 'Spin studio and strength studio', 'Hiking, biking, and walking trails', 'Volleyball court', 'Basketball courts', 'Dog park', 'Catch and release lakes', 'Outdoor fitness zone with climbing wall', 'Caso Santa Rita Ranch', '30°39\'12.2"N 97°49\'18.1"W', 'Managed by Avenue 5 Residential', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Pricing may include current special and is subject to change without notice.']
